{"tid":796513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普宣布 美國與墨西哥就新貿易協定達協議","createTime":"2018-08-27T23:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T06:43:27.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"58cbffa612bf9e71c4b8cf468e5be27e99cf12dc","tid":796513,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T23:09:57.000Z","msg":"川普宣布 美國與墨西哥就新貿易協定達協議<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2533046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2533046&d=gLXFOZz10GvIW1xai%2F2ACp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=4ec7df6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2533046&h=af95934c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2533046</a><br />\n<br />\n〔中央社〕美國總統川普今天表示，美國和墨西哥已就修訂北美自由貿易協定（NAFTA）達成協議，並將稱之為美墨貿易協定。美國可以和加拿大另訂協定，或讓加拿大納入美墨協定。<br />\n<br />\n根據路透社的目擊者，川普表示這項協定對美墨兩國都有利，他並致電墨西哥總統潘尼亞尼托（Enrique Pena Nieto）致賀。<br />\n<br />\n潘尼亞尼托告訴川普，仍希望能將加拿大納入這項協定。川普對此表示，美國和加拿大可以另訂協定，或是讓加拿大加入美墨協定。<br />\n<br />\n川普稍早就推文透露：「似有希望與墨西哥達成重大協議。」墨西哥經濟部長瓜哈爾多（Ildefonso Guajardo）也表示，雙方談判有進展。<br />\n<br />\n在川普堅持下，美國、墨西哥和加拿大已協商1年，以修改有24年歷史的NAFTA。<br />\n彭博報導，3位熟悉談判過程的匿名人士透露，過去幾天美墨雙方已就汽車和能源等棘手議題達成重大突破。"},{"pid":"0929a96d93d009f0384301dc69705e5c3e15ba97","tid":796513,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T23:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2006e365547de9ec546181186034b4e5623d6cc","tid":796513,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T23:23:31.000Z","msg":"支那又贏了"},{"pid":"5282e7660eb54c02b690ef92deff902326568e57","tid":796513,"uid":71768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T23:46:39.000Z","msg":"似乎一人搞一條一帶一路咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9fe5062fddf4a474eef81b577fe12